text: Jimmy Dzingai (born 21 November 1990) is a Zimbabwean footballer who plays as a defender for Yadah Stars F.C. and the Zimbabwe national football team. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:CAPS United players Category:Zimbabwe Premier Soccer League players Category:Zimbabwean footballers Category:Zimbabwe international footballers Category:Association football defenders Category:2019 Africa Cup of Nations players
